      ** AFDPP25 *******************************************
      *  OUTSOURCE BIN NUMBER ASSIGNMENT FILE              *
      *                                                    *
      *  LEC  2021/08/12    CREATE                         *
      ******************************************************
     A          R AFDPP251                  TEXT('BIN ASSIGNMENT')
      *
     A            BNSKJY         1          COLHDG('STATUS')
     A            BNKODT         8  0       COLHDG('STATUS CHANGE DATE')
     A            BNKOTM         6  0       COLHDG('STATUS CHANGE TIME')
     A            BNKOME        15          COLHDG('STATUS CHANGED BY TM')
     A            BNNOBN         3          COLHDG('BIN NUMBER')
     A            BNISDT         8  0       COLHDG('BIN ISSUED DATE')
     A            BNISTM         6  0       COLHDG('BIN ISSUED TIME')
     A            BNISME        15          COLHDG('BIN ISSUED BY TM')
     A            BNLBDT         8  0       COLHDG('BIN LABEL PRINT DATE')
     A            BNLBTM         6  0       COLHDG('BIN LABEL PRINT TIME')
     A            BNLBME        15          COLHDG('BIN LABEL PRINT BY')
      *
     A          K BNNOBN
